Spybot Search and destroy



About Spybot

    * Publisher: PepiMK Software
    * License: Free
    * Minimum requirements: Windows 95/98/Me/NT/2000/XP
    * Uninstaller included?: Yes

This program can detect and remove adware files and modules from your computer such as, Stardialer, Datingbox.nl and Casinopalazzo. Spybot effectively detects spyware, adware, key loggers, Internet dialers, browser hijackers, and some trojan horse programs.
